0x402087 &lt;code+71&gt;:	0x80	0x7f	0x7f	0x89	0x53	0x7f	0xb0	0xe1
0x40208f &lt;code+79&gt;:	0x7f	0xcd	0xb	0x7f	0x7f	0x80	0x7f	0x0
